nodes.text: Darth Vader: Dark Lord of the Sith 23

Darth Vader: Dark Lord of the Sith 23 is the twenty-third issue of the canon comic book series Star Wars: Darth Vader: Dark Lord of the Sith. The issue was written by Charles Soule, illustrated by Giuseppe Camuncoli, and published on November 14, 2018 by Marvel Comics.

"FORTRESS VADER" - PART 5 Darkness rises above MUSTAFAR as the brutal designs of LORD MOMIN begin to take shape. But the planet's inhabitants cannot take this desecration lightly, and shape plans of their own.
